Version 2.0.0 (2026/05/09)
* Added support for weekly reset times and for determining reset times for
  other server regions
  - Renamed the library to LibServerResetTime and renamed all of the functions
    to better reflect what they currently do
  - The original LibDailyResetTime and function names are still supported by a
    compatibility layer that translates the original interface into the new
    interface, so that addons that used LibDailyResetTime can continue to work
    with no code changes (though a manifest change may be necessary)

Version 1.0.1 (2026/03/03)
* Improved the handling of errors arising from the use of the library prior to
  EVENT_ADD_ON_LOADED

Version 1.0.0 (2026/03/02)
* Initial version
